This paper discusses generative neural nets and their connection to statistical physics and information geometry. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information theory (cs.IT), systems and control (cs.SY), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
